<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I agree with the above post about finally being able to out melee the pet!<BR>
<BR>
One of the great things about this weapon is that it does not involve getting on a waiting list for 3 hours to get a chance at it.  I got mine off of a wandering Frost Giant Scout in the Great Divide.  I lost the roll for it, but the guy who won it, GAVE it to me because I was not going to sell it, but use it.  Thanks to Patavian of the Tribunal!<BR>
