<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: G-Shaman</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-12-23 16:26:26</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yes, I agree with above! I am a 52 Shaman on Fennon Ro and I bought one for a little over 5k. The RAGE spell line is now fixed and stacks with most other buffs and this has given some surprising results...<BR>
<BR>
I was hunting with some guildmates in EW and we were killing Warden Burke, who has a VERY high MR so my spells typically don't land. I was the 7th with a 6 person group, so I was ungrouped with my guildmates. There were 2 warriors in the group lev 50 & 51 and several others who did not participate in the Melee. I hadn't had a chance to give ANY buffs to the warriors yet and I was fully buffed with lev 49 stat buffs and Rage and Alacrity (Dex didn't stack with Rage but will on the next patch I hear). We started the melee..and I GOT THE KILL!! hehe. I KSed using melee ONLY from 2 50+ warriors. Im not sure if I just got super lucky or what, but I was the one reading the little yellow letters! Melee is back shaman!!</font></td></tr></table>
